  14,25,It yields its fruits in every season by Allahâ€™s leave. Allah cites these examples for men so that they may learn a lesson from them
  14,26,But the example of an evil word is that of an evil tree which is torn out from the earth and has no stability
  14,27,"With firm words, Allah makes the believers steadfast in the life of this world and in the hereafter; but Allah lets the wrongdoers go astray. Allah does what He pleases"
  14,28,Have you not seen those people who have responded to the favors of Allah with ingratitude and drive their people into the House of Perdition
  14,29,"Which is hell! Wherein they shall burn, an evil place to live"
  14,30,They set up equals with Allah to faces will be covered with flames
  14,31,Allah will requite each soul according to its deeds; surely Allah is swift in taking the account
  14,32,"This is a proclamation for mankind: let them take warning therefrom; let them know that He is the One and Only - worthy of worship - and let the men of understanding learn a lesson"
  14,33,"The sun and the moon are also assigned for your benefit, which steadfastly pursue their courses, to cause the night and the day for your benefit"